text: Nat Geo Kids is a South Korean TV channel dedicated to children of 2 to 7 age. The channel launched on October 1, 2016 as the first Nat Geo Kids feed in the world replacing Cinecanal. As of March 31, 2022, it is the only feed of Nat Geo Kids feed that is airing. Category:Television channels in Asia
title: Nat Geo Kids (South Korean TV channel)
